data.description: This amazing condo located in the gated community of the Villas'' at Green Hills Estates features three bedrooms, three full bathrooms with almost two thousand square feet. As you walk through a black rod iron fence into your private haven . You're drifted into the main entrance door, as this beauty has two main entrances. One is to the private room and the other is the main house. It features high ceilings with lots of windows, including the sky light which gives it an extravagant entrance. The living room has a fireplace with laminate wood floors and unique built in shelving. Kitchen has updated granite counter tops and has lots of cabinet space. The upstairs includes two separate private suites. One being the main bedroom suite. The spacious bathroom includes a dual his and her vanity. A stand up shower plus a separate tub including a huge walk in closet. Across the hallway with beautiful sky light view is the jr suite. Located walking distance to the pool house, the golf course, restaurant plus many more amenities. All of this in a private community. Book your appointment today
